OL,3,CWelsh NHS came 'close to collapse' and
OL,4,Cdoctors had 'no PPE', inquiry finds
OL,6,FHealth services in Wales and the rest
OL,7,Fof the UK "came close to collapse"
OL,8,Fduring the pandemic, the UK Covid-19
OL,9,FInquiry has found.
OL,11,FIn its third report, published on
OL,12,FThursday, the Inquiry said "collapse
OL,13,Fwas only narrowly avoided thanks to
OL,14,Fthe extraordinary efforts" of
OL,15,Fhealthcare workers.
OL,17,FDespite those efforts, it found many
OL,18,FCovid and non-Covid patients received
OL,19,Finadequate care, with some conditions
OL,20,Fbecoming untreatable as a result.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
