CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1773929472
OL,3,CWelsh NHS came 'close to collapse' and
OL,4,Cdoctors had 'no PPE', inquiry finds
OL,6,FHealthcare workers put their own lives
OL,7,Fat risk, with the pandemic having a
OL,8,F"significant and long-lasting impact"
OL,9,Fon their mental health.
OL,11,FThe Inquiry's Chair, Baroness Heather
OL,12,FHallett, has made 10 recommendations
OL,13,Fto ensure the healthcare systems can
OL,14,Fbetter cope with any future pandemics.
OL,16,FShe said: "Healthcare workers carried
OL,17,Fthe burden of caring for the sick in
OL,18,Funprecedented numbers. It came at a
OL,19,Fhuge cost to them, their families,
OL,20,Ftheir patients and the loved ones of
OL,21,Fpatients.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,462,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1773929472
OL,3,CWelsh NHS came 'close to collapse' and
OL,4,Cdoctors had 'no PPE', inquiry finds
OL,6,F"We cannot know when, but there will
OL,7,Fbe another pandemic. My
OL,8,Frecommendations, taken as a whole,
OL,9,Fshould mean that the UK is better
OL,10,Fprepared for that pandemic. In doing
OL,11,Fso, we shall avoid some of the
OL,12,Fterrible human cost of Covid-19."
OL,14,FOn hospital visiting restrictions, the
OL,15,FInquiry criticised the Welsh
OL,16,FGovernment's initial decision not to
OL,17,Fallow fathers to visit pregnant women
OL,18,Fafter birth, and the subsequent delay
OL,19,Fin changing that guidance.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
