CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1773929472
OL,3,CWelsh NHS came 'close to collapse' and
OL,4,Cdoctors had 'no PPE', inquiry finds
OL,6,FIt found the resumption of planned,
OL,7,Fnon-emergency services was "a long way
OL,8,Fbehind" in Wales compared to England
OL,9,Fand Scotland.
OL,11,FWales' decision to pause its cancer
OL,12,Fscreening programmes led to a steep
OL,13,Fdrop in diagnoses in 2020, with missed
OL,14,Fand late diagnoses and longer waits
OL,15,Ffor treatment leading to an increase
OL,16,Fin colorectal cancer deaths.
OL,18,FIn Wales, face masks were advised in
OL,19,Fhealthcare settings from 28 September
OL,20,F2020 but were never mandated.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
