PN,46105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1773929472
OL,3,CWelsh NHS came 'close to collapse' and
OL,4,Cdoctors had 'no PPE', inquiry finds
OL,6,FThe Inquiry found UK stockpiles of PPE
OL,7,Fwere insufficient with many items
OL,8,Fhaving gone out of date.
OL,10,FThen-Chief Medical Officer Dr Andrew
OL,11,FGoodall said the provision of PPE was
OL,12,Fundoubtedly one of the most
OL,13,Fsignificant challenges" in keeping
OL,14,Fhealthcare workers safe.
OL,16,FOne Welsh consultant recalled how "no
OL,17,FPPE was provided" when the virus first
OL,18,Fstarted to spread.
OL,26,@uD@WO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/13
