OL,3,CWelsh NHS came 'close to collapse' and
OL,4,Cdoctors had 'no PPE', inquiry finds
OL,6,FIt comes as mass mask-wearing has re-
OL,7,Femerged in Kent, where two people have
OL,8,Fdied in an outbreak of meningitis.
OL,10,FPublic Health Wales has advised people
OL,11,Fto get vaccinated and be aware of the
OL,12,Fsymptoms but said the disease is rare,
OL,13,Fwith only 19 cases reported in Wales
OL,14,Fin 2024.
OL,16,FA failure to collect data on the
OL,17,Fdeaths of healthcare workers from
OL,18,FCovid in Wales led to a lack of
OL,19,Funderstanding about its severity and
OL,20,Ftransmissability, the Inquiry said.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
