FL,462,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1773929472
OL,3,CWelsh NHS came 'close to collapse' and
OL,4,Cdoctors had 'no PPE', inquiry finds
OL,6,FIt also risked giving the impression
OL,7,Fthat healthcare workers were
OL,8,F"expendable and not valued".
OL,10,FThere were also occasions where
OL,11,Fworkers had to care for their own
OL,12,Fcolleagues with Covid, some of whom
OL,13,Fdied in their care, which was
OL,14,Fdescribed by one Welsh consultant as
OL,15,F"traumatic".
OL,17,FThe Inquiry heard how Wales' field
OL,18,Fhospitals "were too expensive and did
OL,19,Fnot represent value for money".
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
