PN,46108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1773929472
OL,3,CWelsh NHS came 'close to collapse' and
OL,4,Cdoctors had 'no PPE', inquiry finds
OL,6,FThe Welsh Government allocated #166m
OL,7,Fto building temporary hospitals on
OL,8,Fsites including Cardiff's Principality
OL,9,FStadium and Venue Cymru in Llandudno.
OL,11,FHowever, they were largely unused,
OL,12,Fwith just three of the hospitals
OL,13,Freceiving a total of 60 patients.
OL,15,FThe Inquiry also highlighted how the
OL,16,Fhospitals "could never have been
OL,17,Fadequately staffed", and has
OL,18,Frecommended "better planning" to
OL,19,Fassess their effectiveness.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,462,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1773929472
OL,3,CWelsh NHS came 'close to collapse' and
OL,4,Cdoctors had 'no PPE', inquiry finds
OL,6,FThe report highlighted how problems
OL,7,Fwith data systems and record-keeping
OL,8,Fhad an impact on communications with
OL,9,Fclinically extremely vulnerable people.
OL,11,F13,000 of 91,000 shielding letters
OL,12,Fwere sent to the wrong addresses by
OL,13,Fthe Welsh Government.
OL,15,FThe pandemic had a colossal impact on
OL,16,Femergency care, with the Inquiry
OL,17,Ffinding ambulance-hospital handover
OL,18,Fdelays had a "detrimental impact" on
OL,19,Fthe provision of "responsive, safe,
OL,20,Feffective and dignified care" in Wales.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G9/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
