PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1773929472
OL,3,CWelsh NHS came 'close to collapse' and
OL,4,Cdoctors had 'no PPE', inquiry finds
OL,6,FThe Inquiry, which held public
OL,7,Fhearings between October 2022 and
OL,8,FMarch 2026, was set up to examine the
OL,9,Fpandemic's impact, scrutinise the
OL,10,Fresponse and learn lessons for the
OL,11,Ffuture.
OL,13,FThere have been calls for a Wales-
OL,14,Fspecific inquiry, but the Welsh
OL,15,FGovernment has repeatedly rejected the
OL,16,Fidea. The Senedd is scrutinising the
OL,17,Ffindings of the Inquiry.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G11/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,462,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46112
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1773929472
OL,3,CWelsh NHS came 'close to collapse' and
OL,4,Cdoctors had 'no PPE', inquiry finds
OL,6,FThis is the third of 10 reports, with
OL,7,Fthe first two focusing on the UK's
OL,8,Fresilience and preparedness and the
OL,9,Fway governments made decisions.
OL,11,FIn November, the Inquiry found the
OL,12,FUK's response was "too little, too
OL,13,Flate", with devolved administrations
OL,14,Frelying too much on those in
OL,15,FWestminster to lead it.
OL,17,FBut the Chair praised then-First
OL,18,FMinister Mark Drakeford for his
OL,19,F"careful, considered and
OL,20,Fcompassionate" approach.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G12/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
